dc_description_s: This line shapefile depicting bathymetric contour line at 5-meter intervals was created out to the 200 mile Exclusive Economic Zone (EEZ) boundary on the California coast. This file was interpolated from a 200m Teale bathymetric grid with ESRI Spatial Analyst 8.1These data provide coverage for most of the 200 nautical mile Exclusive Economic Zone (EEZ) off the coast of California, identifying depth variations througout the EEZ. These data are not suitable for navigation purposes.
